{
  "stem": "24364.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Boy, I was so sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, we went-- so we decided to go to Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we didn't really know-- I remember they didn't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was all very confusing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the weather was also bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ship was barely moving, because we didn't have enough coal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we never knew whether we were going to make it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, apparently, if I remember, the coast of Cyprus appeared and everyone was rejoicing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody really cared whether the British would see us or not, because we thought we would die.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And British tug boats dragged us into-- into Cyprus, into Limassol harbor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where we stood for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I remember there was a warship which accompanied-- accompanied us to Haifa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we arrived in Haifa sometime in the beginning of December or the end of November.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember the date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we came to Haifa, there was a big ship, a really luxury liner standing in the harbor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was under steam.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were told that we were going to be put on that luxury liner in lieu of a quarantine, because Atlit, which usually served this quarantine, apparently was too busy or they couldn't take us or something like that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't understand why the liner was under steam, but we were told it had to be under steam because of the food and of the water and of all the things that were needed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called the And that's another story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were supposed to be transported or transferred to the within the next couple of days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started with some of our people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
